The paper discusses the management of resources in a distributed environment, which is a key aspect of distributed computing (cs.DC) and distributed systems (cs.Distributed Systems). It also touches upon network infrastructure (cs.NI) and software engineering (cs.SE) aspects of resource management systems. Additionally, the paper discusses the policies and cost models of different organizations, which falls under the category of computer engineering (cs.CE).
